<p>All the arguments except the last are the name of the post and file. The last argument is the category.</p>

<p>It then opens it, as Iâ€™m in OS X, in <del>mac vim. I just hit the keys â€˜Goâ€™ (heh, funny) and start editing.</del> <a href="https://code.visualstudio.com">Visual Studio Code</a>.</p>

